<body>
<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>A large stele (<measure dim="height" unit="metre" type="length">1.46</measure> x <measure dim="width" unit="metre" type="length">0.87</measure> x <measure dim="depth" unit="metre" type="length">0.28</measure>) with a central panel, within simple moulding, topped by a decorated pediment and acroteria and flanked by scrolls. The panel is supported by two winged <rs type="decoration">victories</rs>, holding palms; between them is a smaller figure, with a wheel, identified by Robert as <rs type="decoration">Nemesis</rs>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> within the panel.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p><measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.03-0.04</measure>, clear but irregular; lunate sigma and epsilon.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date exact="none" notAfter="0233" notBefore="0166">Late second/early third century</date>
 (<rs type="criteria">prosopography</rs>).</p>
</div>
